{"tid":871318,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中美洲「移民」攻破墨西哥邊境  特朗普要求先向墨西哥申請庇護","createTime":"2018-10-21T23:59:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T11:37:06.000Z","uid":141151,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"2a320aa594f0676b3dfecaa1f1ad8e0c004cb944","tid":871318,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T23:59:43.000Z","msg":"<strong>拉美移民闖瓜、墨邊境爆衝突<br />\n</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8B%89%E7%BE%8E%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E9%97%96%E7%93%9C-%E5%A2%A8%E9%82%8A%E5%A2%83%E7%88%86%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-160000126.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%258B%2589%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2597%2596%25E7%2593%259C-%25E5%25A2%25A8%25E9%2582%258A%25E5%25A2%2583%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-160000126.html&d=RLcLEq4rWdBVigYxFuaZEqMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=34595c2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8B%89%E7%BE%8E%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E9%97%96%E7%93%9C-%E5%A2%A8%E9%82%8A%E5%A2%83%E7%88%86%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-160000126.html</a><br />\n<br />\n為了前往美國，19日有數以百計的中美洲移民衝破瓜地馬拉與墨西哥邊境的疆籬，強行進入墨國境內，墨西哥鎮暴警察則試圖阻止移民繼續挺進，雙方發生激烈衝突。對移民政策態度強硬的美國總統川普，則在日前聲稱若墨國無法擋下移民，就要出動軍隊關閉美墨邊界。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">根據《紐時》報導，部分群眾朝墨西哥邊境安全警戒線扔擲石塊及其他物品，警方則發射催淚彈，許多移民、墨國警察以及記者在混亂中掛彩。</span><br />\n<br />\n雖然有些移民掉頭返回瓜地馬拉，但仍有數百名男女及孩童留在橫越蘇奇亞提河的大橋上，希望繼續前往美國。川普則於18日明確表態，聲稱墨西哥若無法擋下移民隊伍，將調動軍隊關閉美墨邊界，墨國政府已向聯合國難民事務高級專員公署（UNHCR）求助，請求協助處理移民尋求庇護的案件。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>移民車隊闖關墨西哥 持續北征追求美國夢<br />\n</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E8%BB%8A%E9%9A%8A%E9%97%96%E9%97%9C%E5%A2%A8%E8%A5%BF%E5%93%A5-%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E5%8C%97%E5%BE%81%E8%BF%BD%E6%B1%82%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A2-224400988.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%259A%258A%25E9%2597%2596%25E9%2597%259C%25E5%25A2%25A8%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%2593%25A5-%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%258C%2597%25E5%25BE%2581%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E6%25B1%2582%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%25A2-224400988.html&d=RLcLEq4rWdBVigYxFuaZEqMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=abb5291b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E8%BB%8A%E9%9A%8A%E9%97%96%E9%97%9C%E5%A2%A8%E8%A5%BF%E5%93%A5-%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E5%8C%97%E5%BE%81%E8%BF%BD%E6%B1%82%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A2-224400988.html</a><br />\n<br />\n儘管面對美國總統川普的一連串激烈發言，但數千名宏都拉斯移民在越過河流進入墨西哥之後，21日仍持續他們的漫長而緩慢的路程，朝向美國長途跋涉而去。<br />\n<br />\n雖然墨西哥設法在與瓜地馬拉邊界的橋樑上，阻擋這批移民「車隊」，但許多人跳下蘇奇亞提河(Suchiate River)，利用臨時湊合的木筏入境，並在21日凌晨重新集結北上。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">川普表示，當局「正全力阻止非法外國人越過南部邊界」，「人們必須先在墨西哥申請庇護，如果他們做不到，美國將會拒絕他們。」</span><br />\n<br />\n然而，根據一名聯邦警察指揮官估算，移民車隊中仍有大約3千人從墨西哥那邊繼續前進。這支聯邦警力正在密切監控移民車隊的動靜。<br />\n<br />\n在此同時，包括婦孺在內約有1千名移民，仍受困於墨西哥邊界橋樑附近，希望能從瓜地馬拉合法進入墨西哥。墨西哥當局堅稱，為了入境，這些滯留在橋樑邊的移民必須逐一申請庇護。<br />\n<br />\n在橋樑邊的移民等待處理之際，那些設法到達墨西哥的人則朝向塔帕珠拉城(Tapachula)而去，那是他們前往美墨邊界、至少3千公里長征中的下一站。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">帶著妻小追求美國夢的21歲移民華雷斯(Aaron Juarez)說，「誰都阻止不了我們，我們疲累不堪，但是非常高興，我們團結一致又堅強不已。」</span>"},{"pid":"4aa61c6a240acba7f00600c7f3c1dfc82179b3fb","tid":871318,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:00:41.000Z","msg":"妙呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"423f44924738e971199b2d0f4eb27a284ee5fefb","tid":871318,"uid":210851,"like":4,"dislike":33,"score":-29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:02:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a667b91bfa980e9f6f13380cc634c20000318a4","tid":871318,"uid":143499,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:20:26.000Z","msg":"非法移民仲要大條道理咁屌柒人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲左膠全部腦閉塞，冇人諗過改善墨西哥販毒同貪污問題，出兵敘利亞停止內戰友話唔好，出兵去中東收班ISIS皮又話法西斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到頭來無解決過任何問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之點都好都係Donald Trump嘅錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe10612f9e20525cdafc3db5a9d02f56d8a9a8e1","tid":871318,"uid":51932,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media2.giphy.com/media/jgsGcrYmUl7q0/giphy.gif?cid=4bf119fc5bcd184a63586d6a59b7c1ef\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia2.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FjgsGcrYmUl7q0%2Fgiphy.gif%3Fcid%3D4bf119fc5bcd184a63586d6a59b7c1ef&h=452d81cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97277e526543eeae1df90a027c77ccd9aee1a671","tid":871318,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:26:59.000Z","msg":"德國無上限收容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b4c328a5f0b75950c41111bab429b6a79661c9","tid":871318,"uid":60831,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:27:03.000Z","msg":"偷渡入嚟叫做追尋美國夢"},{"pid":"b4a1419140f42ab219a51c4b13d6be3c1e54e056","tid":871318,"uid":121146,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"19b4c328a5f0b75950c41111bab429b6a79661c9","tid":871318,"uid":60831,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:27:03.000Z","msg":"偷渡入嚟叫做追尋美國夢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:34:14.000Z","msg":"唔收就係種族主義者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fabc7d5beec870d7f714c85a8b82ca0eb3dfff6","tid":871318,"uid":30791,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T00:38:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FoxNews/posts/10157473695306336\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFoxNews%2Fposts%2F10157473695306336&d=RLcLEq4rWdBVigYxFuaZEqMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=87593791\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FoxNews/posts/10157473695306336</a><br />\n<br />\nJason Pollins We should w